// ë¹ˆê°’ ê²€ì‚¬ (ê³µë°±ì„ ì œì™¸í•˜ê³  ë¹ˆê°’ì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkBlank(box) { // boxëŠ” object ex) input, textarea
	var valid = box.value.replace(/\s/gi,"");
	if (valid=="") return true;
	return false;
}

// ë¹ˆê°’ ê²€ì‚¬ (ë©”ì„¸ì§€ ì¶œë ¥ / ê³µë°±ì„ ì œì™¸í•˜ê³  ë¹ˆê°’ì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkBlank_msg(box, msg) {
	var objLength = $(box).length;	

	var valid = box.value.replace(/\s/gi,"");
	
	if (valid=="") {
		if (!msg) msg = "Blank value. Please enter a value."; //ë¹ˆ ê°’ìž…ë‹ˆë‹¤. ê°’ì„ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”.
		
		alert(msg);
		 
		if(objLength == 1){
			box.focus();
		}else{
			box[0].focus();
		}
		
		return true;
	}
	return false;
}

// ë¹ˆê°’ ê²€ì‚¬ (ê³µë°±ì„ ì œì™¸í•˜ì§€ ì•Šê³  ë¹ˆê°’ì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkNull(box) { // boxëŠ” object ex) input, textarea
	if (box.value=="") return true;
	return false;
}

// ë¹ˆê°’ ê²€ì‚¬ (ë©”ì„¸ì§€ ì¶œë ¥ / ê³µë°±ì„ ì œì™¸í•˜ì§€ ì•Šê³  ë¹ˆê°’ì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkNull_msg(box, msg) {
	if (box.value=="") {
		if (!msg) msg = "Blank value. Please enter a value."; //ë¹ˆ ê°’ìž…ë‹ˆë‹¤. ê°’ì„ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”.
		alert(msg);
		box.focus();
		return true;
	}
	return false;
}

// ìˆ«ìžë§Œ ìž…ë ¥ê°€ëŠ¥í•˜ê²Œ
function chkInputNum() {
	if (event != null) {
		var key = event.keyCode;
		if ((key!=13) && (key<48 || key>57)) {
			event.returnValue = false;
			return;
		}
	}
	return;
}

// ìˆ«ìžê°€ ë“¤ì–´ìžˆëŠ”ì§€ ê²€ì‚¬ (ìˆ«ìžê°€ ë“¤ì–´ìžˆìœ¼ë©´ true ìˆ«ìžê°€ ì•ˆë“¤ì–´ìžˆìœ¼ë©´ false)
function chkNumeric(s) {
	var isNum = /\d/;
	if ( !isNum.test(s) ) return false;
	return true;
}

// ìˆ«ìží˜•ì‹ ê²€ì‚¬ (ì „ë¶€ìˆ«ìžë©´ true ìˆ«ìžì•„ë‹Œ ë¬¸ìžê°€ ìžˆì„ ê²½ìš° false)
function chkNum(box) {
	var isNum = /^[\d]+$/;
	if ( box.value.search(isNum) ) return false;
	return true;
}

// ìˆ«ìž í˜•ì‹ ê²€ì‚¬ (ë©”ì„¸ì§€ ì¶œë ¥ / íŠ¹ìˆ˜ë¬¸ìž ì œê±° / type==1 ì´ë©´ ì•žì—ì˜¤ëŠ” 0 ì œê±° : 000012 -> 12)
function chkNum_msg(box,type) {
	var valid = "0123456789";
	if (box.value == '') return;
	var len = box.value.length;

	for (var i=0; i<len; i++) {
		if (valid.indexOf(box.value.charAt(i)) == -1) {
			alert("Enter digits"); //ìˆ«ìžë§Œ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”
			box.value = box.value.substring(0, i); box.focus();
			return;
		}
	}
	if (type==1) {
		var result, ch, flag=0;
		if (len == 0 || box.value == "0" || box.value.charAt(0) != "0") return;
		for (var z=0; z<len; z++) {
			ch = box.value.charAt(z);
			if (ch=="0") {continue;} else {flag=1; box.value = box.value.substring(z); break;}
		}
		if (flag==0) box.value=0;
	}
}

// ê³µë°±(ìŠ¤íŽ˜ì´ìŠ¤)ê²€ì‚¬ (ê³µë°±ì´ ìžˆìœ¼ë©´ true ì—†ìœ¼ë©´ false)
function chkSpace(strText) {
	return (strText.search(/\s/) != -1);
}

// ì²«ê¸€ìž ì˜ë¬¸ ê²€ì‚¬ (ì²«ê¸€ìžê°€ ì˜ë¬¸ì†Œë¬¸ìžì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkOnechar(strText) {
	var isEng = (/^[a-z]*$/g).test(strText.charAt(0));
	if (!isEng) return false;
	return true;
}

// ì˜ë¬¸ í˜•ì‹ ê²€ì‚¬ (ì˜ë¬¸ì´ë©´(ê³µë°±ì¸ì •) true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkEng(strText) {
	var isEng;
	for (var i=0; i<strText.length; i++) {
		isEng = (/^[a-zA-Z\s]*$/g).test(strText.charAt(i));
		if (!isEng) return false;
	}
	return true;
}

// í•œê¸€ê²€ì‚¬ (ì „ë¶€í•œê¸€ì´ë©´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkHangul(strText) {
	for (var i=0; i<strText.length; i++) {
		if (strText.charCodeAt(i)<0xAC00 || strText.charCodeAt(i)>0xD7A3) {
			if ((strText.charCodeAt(i)<12593 || strText.charCodeAt(i)>12643 ) && (strText.charCodeAt(i) != 32)) return false;
		}
	}
	return true;
}

// ë¼ë””ì˜¤ë²„íŠ¼ ì²´í¬ (ì„ íƒëœ ê²ƒì´ true ì•„ë‹ˆë©´ false)
function chkRadio(box) {
	for (var i=0; i<box.length; i++) { if (box[i].checked) return true; }
	return false;
}

// ë¼ë””ì˜¤ë²„íŠ¼ ì²´í¬ (ì„ íƒëœ ê²ƒì´ ìžˆìœ¼ë©´ false ì„ íƒëœ ê²ƒì´ ì—†ìœ¼ë©´ trueê°’ ë¦¬í„´í•˜ê³  ë©”ì„¸ì§€ ì¶œë ¥)
function chkRadio_msg(box, msg) {	
	var cnt = 0;
	
	if(box.length > 1){
		for (var i=0; i<box.length; i++) {
			if (box[i].checked) return false;
		}
	}else{
		if(box.checked){
			return false;
		}
	}
	if (!msg) msg = "Select one or more selections."; //ì„ íƒí•­ëª©ì„ í•˜ë‚˜ ì´ìƒ ì„ íƒí•˜ì‹­ì‹œì˜¤.
	alert(msg);
	box[0].focus();
	return true;
}

function Check_radio(ChkName,intChkNum) {
	var f = document.mail_frm;
	var max = eval("f." + ChkName + ".length");
	for (var j=0; j<max; j++) {
		if (intChkNum != j) {
			eval("f." + ChkName + "[" + j + "].checked = false;");
		}
	}
}

// íŒì—…ì°½ ë„ìš°ê¸°
var _pop //create global variable without assigning a value so that its value is null
function popen(url,name,w,h,scroll,pos,res, menu) { // (ê²½ë¡œ,ì´ë¦„,ê°€ë¡œ,ì„¸ë¡œ,ìŠ¤í¬ë¡¤ìœ ë¬´,ìœ„ì¹˜,ë¦¬ì‚¬ì´ì¦ˆ)

	if (!scroll) scroll = 1;
	if (!pos) pos = "center";
	if (!res) res = 0;
	if (!menu) menu = "no";

	switch (pos) {
		case 'center' :
			LeftPosition = (screen.width) ? (screen.width - w) / 2 : 100;
			TopPosition = (screen.height) ? (screen.height - h - 100) / 2 : 100;
			break;
		case "random" :
			LeftPosition = (screen.width) ? Math.floor(Math.random() * (screen.width - w)) : 100;
			TopPosition = (screen.height) ? Math.floor(Math.random() * ((screen.height - h) - 75)) : 100;
			break;
		default :
			var reg = /_/;
			if(reg.test(pos)) {
				var posArr =  pos.split('_');
				LeftPosition=posArr[0];
				TopPosition=posArr[1];
			}else{
				LeftPosition=0;
				TopPosition=0;
			}
		break;
	}

	var settings = 'width=' + w + ', height=' + h + ', top=' + TopPosition + ', left=' + LeftPosition + ', scrollbars=' + scroll;
	settings += ', location=no, directories=no, status=no, menubar='+menu+', toolbar=no, resizable=' + res;

	if(_pop!=null && !_pop.closed) {
		_pop.close();
	}

	pop = window.open(url, name, settings);
	pop.focus();
}

function pimage(strImgSrc) {
	popen(strImgSrc, 'image_view', '1', '1', '0', '1');
}


function isEmail(str) {
	var email_exp = /^[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+@[-!#$%&\'*+\\/0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+\.[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+$/;
	return email_exp.test(str);
}

// ì´ë©”ì¼ í˜•ì‹ ê²€ì‚¬ (ë§žìœ¼ë©´ true í‹€ë¦¬ë©´ false)
function chkEmail(box) {
	if (chkBlank_msg(box,"Please enter your email")) return false; //ì´ë©”ì¼ì„ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”
	if (chkSpace(box.value)) {
		alert("Please enter your email without the spaces."); //ì´ë©”ì¼ì€ ê³µë°±ì—†ì´ ìž…ë ¥í•´ ì£¼ì‹­ì‹œì˜¤.
		box.value = box.value.replace(/\s/gi,"");
		box.focus(); box.select(); return false;
	}
	var email_exp = /^[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+@[-!#$%&\'*+\\/0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+\.[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+$/;
	if (!email_exp.test(box.value)) {
		alert("E-mail format is not correct."); //ì´ë©”ì¼ í˜•ì‹ì´ ì •í™•í•˜ì§€ ì•ŠìŠµë‹ˆë‹¤.
		box.focus(); box.select(); return false;
	}
	return true;
}

function chkEmail2(box1,box2) {
	if (chkBlank_msg(box1,"Please enter your email")) return false; //ì´ë©”ì¼ì„ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”
	if (chkBlank_msg(box2,"Please enter your email")) return false; //ì´ë©”ì¼ì„ ìž…ë ¥í•˜ì„¸ìš”
	if (chkSpace(box1.value)) {
		alert("Please enter your email without the spaces."); //ì´ë©”ì¼ì€ ê³µë°±ì—†ì´ ìž…ë ¥í•´ ì£¼ì‹­ì‹œì˜¤.
		box1.value = box1.value.replace(/\s/gi,"");
		box1.focus(); box1.select(); return false;
	}
	if (chkSpace(box2.value)) {
		alert("Please enter your email without the spaces."); //ì´ë©”ì¼ì€ ê³µë°±ì—†ì´ ìž…ë ¥í•´ ì£¼ì‹­ì‹œì˜¤.
		box2.value = box2.value.replace(/\s/gi,"");
		box2.focus(); box2.select(); return false;
	}
	var email_exp = /^[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+@[-!#$%&\'*+\\/0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+\.[-!#$%&\'*+\\./0-9=?A-Z^_a-z{|}~]+$/;
	if (!email_exp.test(box1.value + "@" + box2.value)) {
		alert("E-mail format is not correct."); //ì´ë©”ì¼ í˜•ì‹ì´ ì •í™•í•˜ì§€ ì•ŠìŠµë‹ˆë‹¤.
		box1.focus(); box1.select(); return false;
	}
	return true;
}

function chkEmail_select(a, obj) {
	if (obj.value=="ì§ì ‘ìž…ë ¥") {
